                <div class="col-lg-4 transparent-background">
                    <div class="h-100 content-wrapper">
                        <div class="content-body text-center">
                            <h1>What we sell</h1>
                            <br>
                            <br>
                            <p>We supply second handed branded clothes, subjected to thorough quality checks and cleaning processes. Our primary focus is providing the resources and the abilities to give old items a new lease of life. Primary brands included within the Ruckus Peak store will include known brands such as The North Face, Berghaus, RAB and many more.</p>
